            <p>Description: How many minutes a player is projected to play</p>
            <br>
            <p>What to look for: The higher number the better</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <hr>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-4">
            <p><u>WinVsOpponent%</u></p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-8">
            <p>Description: How many minutes a player is projected to play</p>
            <br>
            <p>What to look for: The higher number the better</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <hr>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-4">
            <p><u>Over/Under</u></p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-8">
            <p>Description: How many minutes a player is projected to play</p>
            <br>
            <p>What to look for: The higher number the better. Except for Defense where it's the lower number the better</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <hr>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-4">
            <p><u>CriteriaScore</u></p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-8">
            <p>Description: How many minutes a player is projected to play</p>
            <br>
            <p>What to look for: The higher number the better</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <hr>
        <div class="row">
